data.description: Great opportunity to own this 4 bedroom, 2.5 bathroom home with a screened in pool located in a very safe and quiet community. The location of this property is priceless ! Less then 20 minutes from Disney, and conveniently located to all major highways, shopping centers, restaurants, health and fitness centers, etc.... Walking distance to local shopping! This community is also approved for short term rentals for all investors searching for a property close to the attractions. All information and room sizes should be verified by buyer and or buyer's agent.    $10,000 IN SELLER CONCESSIONS !!!!!! Buyer can use these funds for closing costs or rate buy down program !!
